TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( V_QTDE_HORAS_TRAB> 180, 180, V_QTDE_HORAS_TRAB )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: QTD_HORAS_TRABALHADAS

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF ( IIF ( ISNULL( VALOR_FIXO), 0) >0, (VALOR_FIXO/30) * V_QTDE_DIAS_TRAB, VALOR_FIXO )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: VALOR_MOVIMENTO

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ( DT_AGENDA < SYSDATE AND TRUNC ( DT_AGENDA, 'MM') = TRUNC ( SYSDATE, 'MM' ) ) OR ( DT_AGENDA > SYSDATE AND TRUNC ( DT_AGENDA, 'MM') <> TRUNC ( SYSDATE, 'MM' ) ) , ADD_TO_DATE( DT_AGENDA, 'MM', 1) , TRUNC ( SYSDATE ) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: P_DT_COMPETENCIA

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF ( IND_PROPORCIONAL = 'S', IIF ( TRUNC ( DT_INICIO_ATUACAO, 'MM' ) = TRUNC ( P_DT_COMPETENCIA, 'MM'), TO_DECIMAL(TO_CHAR(DT_INICIO_ATUACAO, 'DD')), 1 ), 1)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_DIA_INI

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF ( TRUNC( DT_FIM_ATUACAO, 'MM') = TRUNC(P_DT_COMPETENCIA, 'MM'), IIF ( TO_DECIMAL (TO_CHAR( DT_FIM_ATUACAO, 'DD') ) = TO_DECIMAL(TO_CHAR ( LAST_DAY(DT_FIM_ATUACAO ), 'DD') ), 30, TO_DECIMAL (TO_CHAR( DT_FIM_ATUACAO, 'DD') ) ), 30 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_DIA_FIM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF ( TRUNC( DT_FIM_ATUACAO,'MM') = TRUNC(P_DT_COMPETENCIA,'MM'), V_DIA_FIM - V_DIA_INI + 1, 30 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_QTDE_DIAS_TRAB

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: ROUND(((HORA_FIXA * 4.5) / 30) * V_QTDE_DIAS_TRAB, 0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_QTDE_HORAS_TRAB
